Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.05,0:22:03.76,Main-207+,Vegapunk,0,0,0,,{Yeah! - OG}Right!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.64,0:22:09.35,Main-207+,Doberman,0,0,0,,{Soldiers on the island! - OG}{Attention, all Marines! - Polly}Attention, all Marines on land!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.72,0:22:14.81,Main-207+,Doberman,0,0,0,,{St. Saturn of the Five Elders\Nwill make landfall on Egghead! - OG}St. Saturn of the Five Elders\Nwill make landfall on Egghead shortly!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.31,0:22:19.53,Main-207+,Vegapunk,0,0,0,,{No one below the rank\Nof commodore may behold him! - OG}{No one below the rank of commodore\Nis permitted to even be in his presence! - Polly}No one below the rank of commodore\Nis permitted to behold him!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.78,0:22:21.99,Main-207+,Marine,0,0,0,,An Elder?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.99,0:22:23.45,Main-207+,Doberman,0,0,0,,{\i1}I repeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.45,0:22:28.03,Main-207+,Doberman,0,0,0,,{\i1}{St. Saturn of the Five Elders\Nwill make landfall on Egghead! - OG}St. Saturn of the Five Elders\Nwill make landfall on Egghead shortly!{Polly - 27:55}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.83,0:22:38.25,Main-207+,Sanji,0,0,0,,{What's that explosion?! - OG}What the hell is up with that explosion?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.84,0:22:42.59,Main-207+,Vegapunk,0,0,0,,{The Five Elders?! One of them\Ncame all the way to this island?! - OG}The Five Elders?! One of them\Ncame all the way to the island?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.59,0:22:43.97,Main-207+,Franky,0,0,0,,{The Five Elders?! - OG}"Five Elders"?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.97,0:22:45.64,Main-207+,Franky,0,0,0,,Who the hell are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.64,0:22:47.68,Main-207+,Vegapunk,0,0,0,,{They're the highest authorities in the world! - OG}Only the highest authority in the world!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.68,0:22:49.10,Main-207+,Franky,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.95,0:23:13.33,Main-207+,Sanji,0,0,0,,{Something's coming out of there! - OG}Something's coming out...!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.73,0:23:40.98,Main-207+,Marine,0,0,0,,{What's that? - OG}What {\i1}is{\i0} that?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.98,0:23:42.48,Main-207+,Marine,0,0,0,,It's a monster...!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.48,0:23:43.40,Main-207+,Marine,0,0,0,,{Cut it out! - OG}Don't say that!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.74,0:23:45.32,Main-207+,Marine,0,0,0,,{That must be... - OG}It has to be...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.12,0:23:55.87,Main-207+,Saturn,0,0,0,,{Solid ground... - OG}The surface...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.46,0:23:59.29,Main-207+,Saturn,0,0,0,,It has been a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.26,0:24:06.47,Main-207+,Bonney,0,0,0,,{What's that monster?! - OG}{What the hell is that thing?! - Polly}Is that some kind of monster?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.64,0:24:09.64,Main-207+,Sanji,0,0,0,,Look up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.64,0:24:10.60,Main-207+,Sanji,0,0,0,,Swerve!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.27,0:24:16.48,Main-207+,Kizaru,0,0,0,,Oops...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.48,0:24:18.69,Main-207+,Kizaru,0,0,0,,That was close...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.69,0:24:20.90,Main-207+,Vegapunk,0,0,0,,Oh no! The island clouds...!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.61,0:24:25.03,Main-207+,Franky,0,0,0,,Kizaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.28,0:24:31.99,Main-207+,Luffy,0,0,0,,{Stop right there! Kizaru! - OG}Hold it right there, Kizaru!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.53,0:24:36.91,Main-207+,Kizaru,0,0,0,,{I think you're reaching\Nyour limit with that form... - OG}You have to be reaching\Nyour limit with that form by now...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.91,0:24:38.92,Main-207+,Franky,0,0,0,,Please, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.92,0:24:42.92,Main-207+,Franky,0,0,0,,Do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.63,0:24:50.47,Main-207+,Luffy,0,0,0,,{Count on– - OG}I'm on it–{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.31,0:25:00.77,Main-207+,Luffy,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.69,0:25:05.73,Main-207+,Luffy,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Star...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.44,0:25:07.15,Main-207+,Luffy,0,0,0,,{\fad(75,75)}Gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.08,0:25:24.17,Thoughts-207+,Kizaru,0,0,0,,{This is no good! - OG}Well now... this isn't good.{Polly}{Well, this is a problem... - Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.88,0:25:31.34,Main-207+,Saturn,0,0,0,,Nika...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.69,0:25:42.48,Main-207+,Luffy,0,0,0,,{I've reached my limit... - OG}Time's up...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.37,0:25:57.70,Main-207+,Franky,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Vegapunk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.70,0:25:59.70,Main-207+,Vegapunk,0,0,0,,{Not to worry. - OG}Not to worry, I'm alright.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.70,0:26:01.71,Main-207+,Sanji,0,0,0,,Atlas{-chan}, are you hurt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.71,0:26:02.67,Main-207+,Atlas,0,0,0,,I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.71,0:26:11.42,Main-207+,Vegapunk,0,0,0,,Are you St. Saturn?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.42,0:26:12.97,Main-207+,Saturn,0,0,0,,{Indeed. - OG}Indeed I am.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.43,0:26:19.89,Main-207+,Saturn,0,0,0,,{I thought you were already dead, Vegapunk. - OG}I was certain we had\Nkilled you already, Vegapunk.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.23,0:26:30.69,Flashbacks-207+,Saturn,0,0,0,,I gave you an order, Vegapunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.20,0:26:41.25,Main-207+,Sanji,0,0,0,,Bonney{-chan}!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.88,0:26:51.26,Flashbacks-207+,Saturn,0,0,0,,{You will not leave him any free will! - OG}You are not to leave him an ounce of free will!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.26,0:26:54.55,Flashbacks-207+,Vegapunk,0,0,0,,{But then Kuma... - OG}But if I do that, then Kuma...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.55,0:26:58.51,Main-207+,Bonney,0,0,0,,St. Saturn!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{=9}===============================DIALOGUE============================
